  "design_notes": "S0: Very easy intro pacing out taps on 4th and 2nd beats, transitioning into slow 4th note onset taps. S1: Safe 4th note patterns following the steady melody and drum beat, without any crossovers or high NPS peaks. S2: A quick 4-beat breather to rest the feet. S3: The main body of the chart, adding holds and rolls to vocal stems and key sustains (10-20% total share), keeping the streams mostly on 4th notes to guarantee casual playability. S4: Sparse outro taps leading to a graceful fadeout.",
